{"tid":2447164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普私下指梅根「不是好人」 　不敢公開講怕與Piers Morgan同一下場","createTime":"2021-03-15T04:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T12:06:06.000Z","uid":271829,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3bb651690c389e8bb38243a7d3a405abfe165a","tid":2447164,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CfrhYFZ4Aob3VA84PDRh0-lgecA=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R6VQJMGUDZEFRL5L6RPZTN2PTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCfrhYFZ4Aob3VA84PDRh0-lgecA%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR6VQJMGUDZEFRL5L6RPZTN2PTA.jpg&h=6cdeed0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國哈里王子和妻子梅根接受美國名嘴奧花雲費專訪，成為一時熱話。曾被梅根批評的美國前總統特朗普，據說看了專訪後私下認為梅根「不是好人」。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n特朗普前顧問米勒（Jason Miller）上特朗普前策士班農（Steve Bannon）的Podcast節目「War Room」，透露特朗普對哈里梅根專訪的想法。米勒說特朗普告訴他：「她不是好人&hellip;&hellip;我以前說過，現在大家看見了。」<br />\n米勒說，特朗普曾想過公開評論專訪，但最終打消念頭，怕會有英國名嘴摩根（Piers Morgan）的下場，成為「取消文化」（cancel culture）下的犧牲品，即因說錯話而要告別公眾視野。<br />\n根據米勒，特朗普說：「大家知道說梅根壞話會被取消，看看摩根就知。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210315/JNWO3KF7LFEPXOJCWF2APBLDN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210315%2FJNWO3KF7LFEPXOJCWF2APBLDN4%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=eae0e888\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210315%2FJNWO3KF7LFEPXOJCWF2APBLDN4%2F&h=a80c24d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210315/JNWO3KF7LFEPXOJCWF2APBLDN4/</a>"},{"pid":"986e284d44677036aa46b6b50bec85f08b26c3a5","tid":2447164,"uid":127575,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"明眼人都知左膠推介唔係好東西<im